HEADWORD: Control theory
<hw>Con*trol" the`o*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Math.,
Engineering)</fld> <def>That branch of Mathematics and Engineering which
deals with the design, identification and analysis of systems with a
view towards controlling them, <it>i. e.</it>, to make them perform
specific tasks or make them behave in a desired way.</def>⟦br⟧
